LaDonna Tittle https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/LaDonna_Tittle 0 LaDonna Marie Tittle (born March 13, 1946) is an American radio personality, model and actress. Tittle is best known for her radio career from the mid–1970s until the early–2000s. Tittle most notable career stints were in Chicago at several stations; WBMX-FM from 1973 to 1978, WJPC-AM alongside Tom Joyner from 1978 until 1989 and WGCI-FM (1992–2000). Since January 2018, Tittle has appeared as Ethel in the Showtime television series The Chi. LaDonna_Marie_Tittle ( born March_13_,_1946 ) is an_American_radio_personality , model_and_actress .
